          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " This is the tunnel underneath the castle that you can crawl through. One side of these tunnels was created by attackers in the mid-1500s, and the other side was created by the castle's defense to intercept the attackers. Daniel went through the tunnel, but I was not comfortable crawling through such a small space![/caption]"
