          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "After our walk by the sea, we walked through the University of St. Andrews. It's a beautiful campus, as I'm sure you can imagine, but it was dark at that point, so I couldn't get many good pictures. I did manage to capture a beautiful stained class window though!"
